UnreachableStatusException - Exception in coreapi
This exception class represents the situation where a client is trying to change the status of an order to a new one, but the conditions for that change are not met.
UnreachableStatusException(String) - Constructor for exception coreapi.UnreachableStatusException
Create a new exception of this type, detailing on the message exactly why the state of the order could not be changed.
